<item>
            <title>[RAT-212] pom.xml license failure when url is https</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/RAT-212</link>
                <project id="12310750" key="RAT">Apache RAT</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;apache-rat-plugin:check fails when the license information in the POM has a url of &quot;https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0&quot;, but not when it has a url of &quot;http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should probably not fail in the case of https.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12941512">RAT-212</key>
            <summary>pom.xml license failure when url is https</summary>
